g.title: j1384419424
g.text: I'm curious about something. But I don't know if you'd be willing to talk about it.

g.title: j1509635248
g.text: Oh, come on. I think it's cute.

g.title: j458053455
g.text: Ask. If I don't want to talk, I won't.

g.title: j636612205
g.text: I have a name already. And a lot of things are cuter than that.

g.title: j1885935805
g.text: What was it like, growing up with Eleanor?

g.title: j670902960
g.text: What brought you here? To Höllvania?

g.title: j2382062729
g.text: You with a five 'o clock shadow. ;)

g.title: j1894475278
g.text: Okay, okay. I'll let it drop.

g.title: j2602757487
g.text: What made you want to be a soldier?

g.title: j387495367
g.text: How'd you get that skana of yours?

g.title: j862448834
g.text: I'd... really rather not get into that.

g.title: j83876574
g.text: Was there something you wanted to talk about?

g.title: j1387859373
g.text: It's a long story. And it's not that I don't trust you, right?

g.title: j2466346301
g.text: Longer answer another time? Over drinks, maybe?

g.title: j460411213
g.text: We've been through some strange things together.

g.title: j1005081858
g.text: There's just a difference between fighting beside somebody...

g.title: j937861805
g.text: Fine, you can use it. Just...keep it between us, all right?

g.title: j47039337
g.text: No, I get it. Maybe another time, then? After I buy you a few rounds first?
